---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — Alan Tapper" description="About Alan Tapper">
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-10">About</h1>

  <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
    <p>
      I'm a Software Engineer at the AT&T AI Foundry, where I architect and develop a scalable
      AI-powered fault resolution workflow serving 2.5 million business customers. My work sits
      at the intersection of backend systems, agentic orchestration, and applied ML — building
      infrastructure that's reliable at scale.
    </p>
    <p>
      I graduated from Rice University with a BA in Computer Science and a BS in Mathematics.
      While there, I served as President of Hanszen College, one of Rice's eleven residential
      colleges, leading our elected student government and advocating for students across campus.
      I'm currently pursuing an M.S. in Computer Science at Georgia Tech, expected 2027.
    </p>
    <p>
      Previously, I interned at Paycom as a Software Developer, where I built a full-stack
      Territory Visualization Tool that transformed how the sales team operated. I also run my
      own tutoring business, working with college, high school, and middle school students in
      Mathematics, Computer Science, Physics, Chemistry, and Latin.
    </p>
    <p>
      Outside of work, I play soccer, water polo, ultimate frisbee, and table tennis. I play
      violin and piano, produce music, and do transcription. I also speedcube and juggle.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 border-t border-gray-100 pt-10">
    <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-8">Experience</h2>
    <div class="space-y-10">

      <div>
        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-1">
          <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Software Engineer</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 shrink-0 ml-4">Jul 2024 – present</span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">AT&T AI Foundry — Atlanta, GA</div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600 list-disc list-outside ml-4">
          <li>Led architecture and development of an AI-powered customer support platform serving 2.5M business customers and processing 300K+ incidents monthly; projected to save ~$20M annually.</li>
          <li>Architected agentic workflows in Python and LangGraph to analyze network diagnostics, identify root causes, and resolve issues automatically.</li>
          <li>Led a major rewrite of a platform's core business logic, improving test-plan accuracy from ~80% to 98% — contributing to ~$100M in projected business value.</li>
          <li>Organization-wide LangSmith and AI evaluation SME, supporting 15+ teams and 100+ engineers; delivered training, consulting, and documentation on AI engineering best practices.</li>
          <li>Led technical delivery across a six-engineer team; mentored 10+ engineers and helped scale the org from 7 to 100+ people.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-1">
          <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Software Developer Intern</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 shrink-0 ml-4">May – Aug 2023</span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Paycom — Grapevine, TX</div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600 list-disc list-outside ml-4">
          <li>Built an internal Territory Visualization Tool (React/TS, PHP/Mezzio, MySQL) that eliminated sensitive data exports to vendors and improved sales territory precision 600x.</li>
          <li>Created analytics and reporting capabilities to help balance sales representatives' workloads.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-1">
          <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Automations Developer Intern</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 shrink-0 ml-4">May – Aug 2022</span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Altium Packaging — Atlanta, GA</div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600 list-disc list-outside ml-4">
          <li>Automated user management, approval workflows, security policy enforcement, and reporting for internal financial systems using UiPath RPA.</li>
          <li>Produced network architecture diagrams, video demos, and software documentation.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 border-t border-gray-100 pt-10">
    <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-6">Skills</h2>
    <dl class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <dt class="w-32 shrink-0 text-gray-400">Languages</dt>
        <dd>Python, Java, JavaScript / TypeScript, SQL</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <dt class="w-32 shrink-0 text-gray-400">Backend</dt>
        <dd>REST / SOAP APIs, concurrent systems, OOP design patterns</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <dt class="w-32 shrink-0 text-gray-400">Frameworks</dt>
        <dd>FastAPI, Angular, LangGraph, LaunchDarkly</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <dt class="w-32 shrink-0 text-gray-400">AI / ML</dt>
        <dd>RAG, vector embeddings, agentic orchestration, model evaluation, prompt engineering, monitoring</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <dt class="w-32 shrink-0 text-gray-400">DevOps</dt>
        <dd>Docker, Kubernetes, Azure DevOps, Git</dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-10 border-t border-gray-100 pt-10">
    <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-6">Now</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
      <li>Working on: AI fault resolution at AT&T AI Foundry</li>
      <li>Teaching: tutoring in Math, CS, Physics, Chemistry, and Latin</li>
      <li>Playing: soccer, water polo, ultimate frisbee, table tennis</li>
      <li>Making: violin, piano, music production</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-10">
    <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-6">Links</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
      <li><a href="https://github.com/alan-tapper" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">GitHub</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alan-tapper/" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">LinkedIn</a></li>
      <li><a href="mailto:tapper.alan@gmail.com" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">Email</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Base>
